<Topics>
	<Topic Name="MISC_FIRST_CONTACT">
		<Dialogue>
			<Speaker Name="Drengin">1</Speaker>
			<Listener Name="Human">0</Listener>
			<Phrase>
				<Morality>2</Morality>
				<Text>You may have defeated the Precursor army, but the war has weakened your forces.

Crushing the once-mighty humans will be a swift and effortless exercise, [YourLeaderName].</Text>
			</Phrase>
		</Dialogue>
		<Dialogue>
			<Speaker Name="Arcean">3</Speaker>
			<Listener Name="Human">0</Listener>
			<Phrase>
				<Morality>1</Morality>
				<Text>[YourLeaderName], the situation is dire. War has left our home sector undefended, and now the Yor and Drengin forces have united to attack Arcea.
The Arcean Empire is in danger of being destroyed by this monstrous alliance. Please, my human friend... help us any way you can.</Text>
			</Phrase>
		</Dialogue>
		<Dialogue>
			<Speaker Name="Altarian">2</Speaker>
			<Listener Name="Human">0</Listener>
			<Phrase>
				<Morality>0</Morality>
				<Text>And now the true war begins. With the Dread Lords defeated, we can focus on the true villains.

To war, cousin!
</Text>
			</Phrase>
		</Dialogue>
		<Dialogue>
			<Speaker Name="Torian">4</Speaker>
			<Listener Name="Human">0</Listener>
			<Phrase>
				<Morality>0</Morality>
				<Text>We will not let the Drengin enslave the galaxy like they once did to the Torians. They will fall and our united forces will stand triumphant!</Text>
			</Phrase>
		</Dialogue>
		<Dialogue>
			<Speaker Name="Yor">5</Speaker>
			<Listener Name="Human">0</Listener>
			<Phrase>
				<Morality>2</Morality>
				<Text>The Dread Lords were weaker than first assumed. Now, the battle falls on us! We will triumph over you weak fleshlings.</Text>
			</Phrase>
		</Dialogue>
		<Dialogue>
			<Speaker Name="Iconian">9</Speaker>
			<Listener Name="Human">0</Listener>
			<Phrase>
				<Morality>0</Morality>
				<Text>The Dark Arnor have fallen, but evil still remains in the galaxy. Let us save the Arceans before it is too late.</Text>
			</Phrase>
		</Dialogue>
